# 🚨 Helmet Violation Detection System

A real-time helmet violation detection system using **YOLOv8**, **Streamlit**, and **PaddleOCR**.

This app detects:
- Motorcyclists **without helmets** inside a defined area
- Automatically captures and **logs number plates** for violators

---

## 🔧 Features

- 🎥 **Live Detection** via Webcam or Uploaded Video
- 🧠 **YOLOv8** for detecting helmets and number plates
- 🔤 **PaddleOCR** for number plate recognition
- 🗺️ Polygonal **Zone-based detection**
- 📝 Fine Logging:
  - Vehicle number
  - Date and Time
  - Snapshot of number plate
- 📁 CSV Export of fine log
- 📸 Image preview of all captured number plates

---

## 🖥️ Interface (Streamlit)

- **Sidebar**: Live Violation History
- **Main View**:
  - Live/resumed video feed
  - Fine log table
  - Download button
  - Number plate snapshots

---

## 🧰 Installation

Make sure Python 3.8+ is installed.

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/helmet-fine-detection.git
cd helmet-fine-detection
